# hacker hive

    sets of hives sharing purpose.
    that's a hive.
    
    hives prototyping life hacks.
    that's the hacker hive.
    
    Berkeley students thriving.
    that's the hacker hive in Berkeley.

the hacker hive is an initiative to make housing cooperatives (like [BSC](http://bsc.coop)) modeled after [hackerspaces](http://hackerspaces.org/wiki/List_of_Hacker_Spaces). we invite all hackers of Berkeley (see [Hack@Berkeley](http://hackersatberkeley.com/), [CSUA](http://www.csua.berkeley.edu/), [OCF](https://secure.ocf.berkeley.edu/), [IEEE](http://ieee.berkeley.edu/), and probably you) to join us in making a cooperative living system near the [northside of UC Berkeley](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Northside,_Berkeley,_California).

